vehicle veers sharply to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Hood Latch Pin Corrosion and Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion and failure of the area around the plate that holds the hood latch pin in place can cause the hood to fly open while driving, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The hood latch pin is loose
the hood latch pin is corroded
the hood latch pin is cracked
the hood flies open while driving.
